<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Create a Game Room</title>
    <style>
        /* Page Styling */
        *{
            padding:0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            
        }


        .home{

            margin:80px auto;

            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap:0px;
            column-gap: 20px;
            padding:0px 20px;

        }

/*login form */

.login-container {
    max-width: 400px;
    width:80%;
    min-width:300px;
    margin: auto;
    background: #e8f5e9; /* Light Green */
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1 {
    color: #2e7d32; /* Dark Green */
}

p {
    color: #388e3c; /* Medium Green */
}

.google-login-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #4caf50; /* Green */
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.google-login-btn img {
    width: 20px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    border-radius: 100%;
    width:30px;
    height:30px;
}

.tips-section {
    margin-top: 30px;
    background: #c8e6c9; /* Light Green */
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.tips-section h2 {
    color: #2e7d32;
}

.tips-section ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.tips-section li {
    color: #388e3c;
    margin: 5px 0;
}




.container {
    max-width: 400px;
    width:97vw;
    min-width:300px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    margin: auto;
    margin-top: 80px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative; /* Required for ::before positioning */
}

/* Overlay Effect */
.container::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(200, 230, 201, 0.404); /* Semi-transparent green */
    border-radius: 12px;
    pointer-events: all; /* Fully blocks interaction */
   
}
.container.no-overlay::before {
    content: none; /* Removes the overlay */
}

        /* Form Styling */
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        select, input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Submit Button */
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #e68900;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="home">
        <% if (!user) { %>
            <div class="login-container">
                <h1>Play the Best Games After Signing In</h1>
                <p>Unlock exclusive mystery games and compete with the best detectives!</p>
        
                <a href="/auth/google" class="google-login-btn">
                    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTsn_7YWUcHfdiZW2UrAM4XFj_2vk2Opk4mVA&s" alt="Google Logo"> Sign in with Google
                </a>
        
                <div class="tips-section">
                    <h2>üîç Mystery Game Tips</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Observe small details ‚Äì they often hold the biggest clues!</li>
                        <li>Think like a detective: Who benefits from the crime?</li>
                        <li>Take notes and connect the dots before making a guess.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <script>
                 document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            document.querySelector(".container").classList.add("no-overlay"); // Removes the ::before
        });
            </script>
        <% } %>
        



    <div class="container">
        <h2>Create a Game Room</h2>
        <form action="/createroom" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="gameGenre">Select Game Genre</label>
                <select id="gameGenre" name="game">
                    <option value="Battle Royale">Battle Royale</option>
                    <option value="Speed Racer">Speed Racer</option>
                    <option value="Mind Bender">Mind Bender</option>
                    <option value="Lost in Jungle">Lost in Jungle</option>
                    <option value="Zombie Hunt">Zombie Hunt</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="maxPlayers">Number of Players</label>
                <input type="number" id="maxPlayers" name="players" min="2" max="7" value="2">
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Create Room</button>
        </form>
    </div>

</div>

    

</body>
</html>
